\begin_inset Formula \[
\sigma=\frac{\sqrt{10^{\atf_{min}/10}-1}}{\drf(\omega_{s})}=\frac{\sqrt{10^{\atf_{max}/10}-1}}{\drf(\omega_{g})}\]

\end_inset 


